<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l7">des Juden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc / Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l8"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> bey <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> ſelbs <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> kürcʒlıch ein antwurt <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l9">tun . Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
