<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>vicztu<ex>m</ex></expan>, als ir uns aber
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Yosep Püczels des juden
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> selbs
                                <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> kürczlich ein antwurt
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> tun. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
